==文化考察==
辰在[[二十八宿|二十八宿]]的對應星宿是[[亢宿|亢宿]]（亢金龍），但也有學者認為辰對應了了[[心宿|心宿]]（即[[天蝎座|天蝎座]]的一部分），傳說中[[心宿二|心宿二]]是蒼龍的心，故生肖為龍<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://linguistics.berkeley.edu/~rscook/socrates/public_html/html/LTBA-18.2.html|author=Richard S. Cook|title=The Etymology of Chinese Chen|journal=''Linguistics of the Tibeto-Burman Area''|publisher=[[University_of_California,_Berkeley|University of California, Berkeley]]|publication-date=Fall 1995|volume=18|issue=2|date=Spring 1997|pages=250|lccn=82-640813|issn=0731-3500|oclc=4790670|access-date=2020-11-03|archive-date=2020-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130095720/http://linguistics.berkeley.edu/~rscook/socrates/public_html/html/LTBA-18.2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[泰國|泰國]]、[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]、[[寮國|寮國]]、[[緬甸|緬甸]]及[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]所用的[[佛曆|佛曆]]中， 龍則為[[那伽|那伽]]所取代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thaiguidetothailand.com/magic-and-superstition/year-of-the-dragon-naga-thai-zodiac/|title=Year of the Dragon - Naga - Thai Zodiac|publisher=''Thai Guide to Thailand''|accessdate=2017-06-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708104841/http://www.thaiguidetothailand.com/magic-and-superstition/year-of-the-dragon-naga-thai-zodiac/|archivedate=2017-07-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>；在[[古隆族|古隆族]]文化中，此生肖則是[[鷹|鷹]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ecs.com.np/culture/tamu-gurung-losar-festival|title=Tamu (Gurung) Losar Festival|publisher=''ECS Nepal''|date=2010-07-11|accessdate=2017-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729174053/http://ecs.com.np/culture/tamu-gurung-losar-festival|archive-date=2017-07-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；在[[波斯|波斯]]文化中為[[鯨|鯨]]；在[[古突厥|古突厥]]曆法中則為[[魚|魚]]。

